observations.recommendation:
We recommended and the Local Chief Executive agreed to: 

direct the Inventory Team to conduct physical count and prepare the Report on the Physical Count of Property, Plant and Equipment (RPCPPE) and submit a copy thereof to the Audit Team; 

require the Accounting and Treasury Offices to prepare and update PPE ledger cards for each PPE sub-account so that general ledger balances of PPE are supported by independent and reliable records; 

instruct the Accounting Office to exert best effort to secure the necessary documents and reports so that appropriate depreciation can be provided; and 

direct the Municipal Treasurer and Municipal Accountant to recover the records that would determine the carrying value of the demolished structure and thereafter derecognize them in the books of the Municipality.
